Power Modes (Value - Description)

  • 0 - Online (default)
  • 1 - Low power (airplane) mode
  • 2 - Factory test mode
  • 3 - Offline
  • 4 - Reset
  • 5 - Power off
  • 6 - Persistent low power (airplane) mode
